ui-editor.description: A modern WYSIWYG editor (based on Quill with built-in extension features).

ui-collapse.description: A content area which can be collapsed and expanded.

ui-alert.description: Alerts provide contextual feedback messages for typical user actions with the handful of available and flexible alert messages.

ui-skeleton.description: Skeleton provide a placeholder while you wait for content to load, or to visualise content that doesn't exist yet.
